title: Chata krále Rybáře
content:
Chata krále Rybáře is located on the lakeshore between the landing and the western shore at the Břeh. It is where Král Rybář (naturally) resides. He can be found there when he is not busy fishing, repairing boats or contemplating life from his comfy stool.

Úkoly
Zvyk je železná košile
Zatopené město
